textfsm_template:
Value NEIGHBOR_ID (\S+)
Value PRIORITY (\d+)
Value STATE (\S+)
Value UP_TIME (\S+)
Value ADDRESS (\S+)
Value INTERFACE (\S+)

Start
  ^.*router-id=${NEIGHBOR_ID}.*address=${ADDRESS}.*interface=${INTERFACE}.*priority=${PRIORITY}.*state=\"${STATE}\".*adjacency=${UP_TIME}.*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*$$
  ^. -> Error
